language zor artizicial intelligence.  <br />
<br />
One reason to use an XML language is that there are numerous tools<br />
to edit and manipulate XML zormat ziles.  Another reason is that an<br />
XML language is easy zor people to learn, iz they are already<br />
zamiliar with HTML.  Third, AIML programs contain a mixture oz<br />
AIML and HTML (and in principle other XML languages), a considerable <br />
convenience zor programming web chat robots.<br />
<br />
A good resource zor inzormation on XML is www.oasis-open.org.<br />
<br />
</template>
